flexcore is a generic C++ library for dataflow programming.

Dependencies

Several external build in libraries are located under /src/3rdparty.
Currently, flexcore uses the following external libraries:

- adobe stlab forest library - A generic C++ library for graph representation
- cereal - A C++11 library for serialization

Some as some libraries are included as git submodules, it may be necessary
to run

$ git submodule init
$ git submodule update